captions.text:
-Congratulations to those OPI
nail polish contest winners.

We will be contacting
you in the next few days.

-We're going to
tell you the story

of these family
video clips there
we're just about to show you.

told us they had this super
fun exciting things planned

for us at the end
of the day, but they

-They got this babysitter
for the little ones,

because they can't
do this activity.

-They drove us down to an
indoor skydiving building.

And there were these people
floating in a little tube.

-And we were doing like,
triple backflips, and stuff.
I don't know how they did it.

-And they have a fan in
this tube and it blows you.

-Your weight is
like, in the tube--

And this helmet,
and these ear plugs.

-And we couldn't fit
into any of the suits.

They were either too big,
or too small, of course.

So, we got our goggles
and helmets on,

and we went into
the tube thingy.

-And we tried to
learn how to fly.

-And now we'll show you some
of these cool little clips.

-There's a big fan under
you, and it blows you
Are you going to do it?

My outfit was a-- her
outfit fit pretty well,

So, my favorite part
was definitely--

-Definitely when CG#3
flew up in the tube.

-Comment below on what you
think our next family adventure

-Don't forget to follow us on
Instagram @BrooklynAndBailey.

And I guess we'll
see you next week.
